.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, drama, fantasy, horror, time-travel
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, iced-tea, water, hot-chocolate, 7up
 1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching horror movies is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
10. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##7
11. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
14. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
15. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
16. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
17. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | time-travel | fantasy | horror     | drama      | disaster |
| Beverage           | sprite         | iced-tea        | hot-chocolate   | water | tea | 7up    |

