.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, lemonade, soy-milk, tea, water
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: rock, funk, hip-hop, house, disco, dubstep
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 4. the fan of funk is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 5. the person drinking cola is not the fan of rock##6
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 7. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 9. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
10. the fan of disco is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
11. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
12. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
13. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
14. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | tea        | soy-milk | water    | cola    | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre      | funk | disco  | dubstep | house | rock | hip-hop      |

