 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
 2. the person drinking milk is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
 5. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 9. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
11. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
14. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking sprite##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2       |       3        |    4     |        5        |    6     |
