 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 6. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person eating tomato##7
 7. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person eating watermelon##7
 9. the person eating watermelon is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
