.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: punk, jazz, indie, d&b, blues, gospel
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, skateboard, train, tram, trike
 1. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of indie##1
 2. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 5. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 6. the fan of punk is between the fan of blues and the person driving the boat##2
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 9. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person driving the motorbike##7
13. the fan of blues is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre         | jazz   | blues | punk      | d&b | gospel  | indie   |
| Transport   | train | trike  | motorbike | boat   | tram | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, badminton, snowboarding, basketball, water-polo
The people have 6 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, fisherman, journalist, project-manager, scientist
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the journalist and the dressmaker##7
 5. the scientist is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is the project-manager##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
 8. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 9. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
10. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
11. the scientist is on the right of the fisherman##1
12. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
13. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is badminton##7
14. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
15. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Sport   | badminton         | snowboarding | rugby | sailing   | water-polo | basketball  |
| Job     | project-manager | journalist  | fisherman  | scientist | dressmaker  | accountant |

 